{"tid":747974,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"林寶堅尼逆線停水街　揭司機酒駕被捕","createTime":"2018-07-19T00:10:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T06:08:11.000Z","uid":81228,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"8417a5002a5e7bce69f0f2b37703ff3b9d5544e7","tid":747974,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T00:10:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180719/photo/bkn-20180719024017938-0719_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180719050931\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180719%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180719024017938-0719_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180719050931&h=0947f5f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n涉酒駕司機一名男親友將「細牛」駛離現場。(李國健攝)<br />\n<br />\n今日(19日)凌晨1時許，警員巡邏期間，發現一輛藍色林寶堅尼Gallardo 跑車（俗稱細牛）逆線停泊於西區副食品批發市場對出水街影線上，男司機於車內疑似熟睡，警員拍醒司機，發現他滿身酒氣，疑酒後駕駛，遂召交警到場替司機進行酒精呼氣測試，證實超標。33歲姓黎男子涉嫌酒駕駛被捕，帶署扣查。<br />\n<br />\n警員調查期間，黎的一名30餘歲男親友接報到場，經了解事件後，將「細牛」駛離現場。<br />\n<br />\n根據運輸署資料顯示，涉事林寶堅尼跑車於2009年首次登記，車主為一名姓黎男子，報住屯門寶田邨。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180719/photo/bkn-20180719024017938-0719_00822_001_02b.jpg?20180719050931\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180719%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180719024017938-0719_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20180719050931&h=51595cdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林寶逆線停泊，警揭男司機酒駕。(李國健攝)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180719/bkn-20180719024017938-0719_00822_001.html?refer=hn2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180719%2Fbkn-20180719024017938-0719_00822_001.html%3Frefer%3Dhn2&d=t02RsGHW0EFmS7pV%2BRgJ%2BwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=556c5306\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180719/bkn-20180719024017938-0719_00822_001.html?refer=hn2</a>"},{"pid":"40f2e4c6521a5906f3fadbda79d529b0090bef16","tid":747974,"uid":120458,"like":179,"dislike":0,"score":179,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T00:12:48.000Z","msg":"車主為一名姓黎男子，報住屯門寶田邨。"},{"pid":"c205f305aea8a28f2240c18a49c8cbc67e58bffc","tid":747974,"uid":28052,"like":90,"dislike":2,"score":88,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T00:15:56.000Z","msg":"有林寶都住公屋？"},{"pid":"8f307cb379d67d827b9952e7a26b1d73ff885c18","tid":747974,"uid":108236,"like":108,"dislike":1,"score":107,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T00:17:10.000Z","msg":"林寶住寶田 好合理呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c10b821be06b5a940b7ae594fa9c4c355672af4b","tid":747974,"uid":51105,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"quote":{"pid":"c205f305aea8a28f2240c18a49c8cbc67e58bffc","tid":747974,"uid":28052,"like":90,"dislike":2,"score":88,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T00:15:56.000Z","msg":"有林寶都住公屋？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T00:19:17.000Z","msg":"寶田以前仲要係中轉屋<br />\n出名多痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0347ddca81a1e574de2f30e75c57e8f7260104c8","tid":747974,"uid":2267,"like":8,"dislike":11,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T00:19:35.000Z","msg":"寶田邨，一個己割讓畀大陸嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fac9ac84a509e0eec9af4f0d0b176b26f70ad13","tid":747974,"uid":6959,"like":50,"dislike":2,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T00:22:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6fe28864b84ffa4a756fabc88d3e7c65b25f37fe","tid":747974,"uid":77569,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T00:23:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"182ea3c6b7185fd20470c40eb06cb250bf604232","tid":747974,"uid":7343,"like":7,"dislike":9,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T00:28:58.000Z","msg":"不嬲住公屋先係富豪"},{"pid":"9009afd1146e73cc787c5d653b886e64efbf1f99","tid":747974,"uid":52942,"like":25,"dislike":35,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"c205f305aea8a28f2240c18a49